<section class="sign-up-faq">
  <div class="container-xxl sign-up__container">
    <h2 class="sign-up-benefits__title">FAQ's</h2>
    <div class="sign-up-benefits__list">
      <div class="sign-up-benefits__item">
        <h3 class="sign-up-benefits__item-title">How does the Trade discount work?</h3>
        <div class="sign-up-benefits__item-desc">
          Trade and contract program members receive special discounts on our portfolio of brands and early
          access to new arrivals. Members receive tax-exempt purchasing privileges at our showrooms and a
          progressive trade discount scaled to volume of purchase.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sign-up-benefits__item">
        <h3 class="sign-up-benefits__item-title">How do I apply for membership?</h3>
        <div class="sign-up-benefits__item-desc">
          New members of our program fill out a simple application form and upload a W-9, plus a resale
          certificate for verification and tax purposes.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sign-up-benefits__item">
        <h3 class="sign-up-benefits__item-title">Is there a minimum order quantity?</h3>
        <div class="sign-up-benefits__item-desc">
          No minimum order is required. Bigger discounts are offered on larger orders.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sign-up-benefits__item">
        <h3 class="sign-up-benefits__item-title">How do I connect with an IDI Trade Representative?</h3>
        <div class="sign-up-benefits__item-desc">
          As soon as you fill out the program application, our representative will be in contact to assist
          you.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sign-up-benefits__item">
        <h3 class="sign-up-benefits__item-title">Are fabric and material samples available?</h3>
        <div class="sign-up-benefits__item-desc">
          Once your membership is registered and approved, you have full access to our extensive sample
          and swatch library.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sign-up-benefits__item">
        <h3 class="sign-up-benefits__item-title">What are my shipping options? Is White Glove Delivery
          available?</h3>
        <div class="sign-up-benefits__item-desc">
          Your furniture will be delivered on time and in perfect condition just the way you ordered it.
          You receive exceptional customer care whether you choose full-service, white glove delivery, our
          economical standard curbside service, or upgrade your standard service to Room-of-Choice. We
          ensure your order is handled perfectly. Please note that online orders can only be shipped
          within the 48 continental United States
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>